# OFM Agent Skills (DAILY)

Read `skill-library` skill when task type is unclear. Manifest: `docs/OFM-SKILL-PLAN.md`.

## Always prefer for this repo

| Domain | Skills |
|--------|--------|
| SEO / GA4 / GSC / blog | `ofm-seo-analytics`, `ofm-deep-site-audit`, `article-writing` |
| UI polish / review | `make-interfaces-feel-better`, `web-design-guidelines` |
| React / Next.js 16 | `vercel-react-best-practices`, `react-patterns`, `frontend-patterns`, `nextjs-turbopack` |
| Complex / 3D animation | `ofm-animation-mastery` (router) |
| Hero GSAP / scroll | `ofm-premium-motion` + user GSAP (`gsap-react`, `gsap-scrolltrigger`) |
| Framer / gestures / transitions | `framer-motion-animator`, `animation-designer`, `motion-ui` |
| Three.js / R3F / WebGL | `threejs-*`, `react-three-fiber` (lazy-load; mobile lite) |
| CTA / form / calculator | `ofm-conversion-audit` |
| API / secrets | `security-review`, `backend-patterns` |

## Ignore unless explicitly requested

Off-stack ECC rules (java-*, perl-*, django-*, rust-*, php-*, etc.) — this repo is Next.js + TypeScript only.

## After substantive code changes

- Run `npm run build`
- Invoke `ecc-react-reviewer` for component changes
- Invoke `ecc-seo-specialist` for meta/copy/sitemap changes
